    "Machine learning is employed with three classifiers: decision tree, random forest, and SVM.",
    "Among them, random forest achieved a maximum classification accuracy of 92.59%.",
    "SVM-based dysgraphia diagnosis systemsSVM is a machine learning algorithm used for both classification and regression tasks, with a focus on enhancing prediction accuracy.",
    "SVM operates by categorizing each class in a high-dimensional space using one or more hyperplanes.",
    "By leveraging labeled input training data, the SVM algorithm constructs an optimal hyperplane for classifying new test data."
